{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no-- we kept that separated, and I have no knowledge of particulars of what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt-- first of all, I felt awful, specifically when it was a Jewish person, which was most of the time-- that one brother can do this to another brother.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as far as for practical purposes, all I was doing was trying to protect my body that the hurt should be the least-- I mean, with my hands, covering my face and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, most of the time when you were beaten, in many, many of these cases, they would make you bend down and take 25 lashes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it wasn't so simple to protect yourself from that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact-- I'm coming back now to the-- to the discussion of Lublin Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mentioned that before, to you, that our whole-- doing was going around faith, praying, whenever you had the chance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Within a week that I was there-- and I constantly had my prayer book in the hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whenever I could, I was saying the Psalms at the-- at the place, and I was caught by one of the SS guards.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he took me in front of all the guys there, and he made me bend down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says he's going to give me 25 lashes, and I have to count.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And trying to maintain a little kind of a humor in the misery, in the middle of the counting, as much as it was hurting, I uttered some Jewish words, which was a cuss word towards him.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all the guys who were assembled to watch there, broke out into laughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he wanted to know what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
